symptoms: smoke or flames appearing from the steering column or under the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slippage and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or jump out of gear, leading to accidents, property damage, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of gear
the vehicle jumps out of gear into reverse or another gear
the transmission fails to engage or disengage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft and U-joint can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or break down, leading to accidents, property damage, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
Engine stalling can cause loss of power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially when driving at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: the vehicle hesitates or struggles to accelerate
the vehicle requires excessive throttle input to maintain speed
